Project Director
	•	PhD in Cognitive Futures
	•	Previously declared three “final” breakthroughs

Chief Embodiment Officer (CEbO)
	•	Specializes in attaching software to limbs

Senior Loop Analyst
	•	Ensures outcomes resemble inputs

Ethics Liaison (Rotational)
	•	Appears during funding rounds

Junior Reality Suppression Associate
	•	Removes inconvenient benchmarks

