⸻

6. Impact Assessment

The Recursive Robotics Initiative delivers measurable outcomes:
	•	Renewed optimism
	•	Familiar disappointment
	•	Excellent demo videos

Long-term societal impact remains undefined but confidently projected.

⸻

7. Conclusion (Non-Binding)

In conclusion, the RRI affirms that humanity has not stalled, regressed, or failed. Instead, it has achieved circular transcendence—a state in which every technological leap lands gracefully on its own origin point.

We now possess intelligence powerful enough to reason abstractly about the universe, yet we continue to express it as a cheerful robot with buttons and shoes. This is not irony. This is alignment.

The future does not repeat itself.
It iterates.

